<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Hatak okcha̱ya ma</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hatak okcha̱ya ma!
 Himak a fehna ka
 Chimi shilombish fehna ka
 Ish anukfillashke.

[V2]
 Chim ishilombish a̱
 Ish kaiyancha chi̱ cho?
 Chim ishilombish fehna kʋt
 Holitopa hoke.

[V3]
 Nana toshbi yona
 Aiʋlli tok keyu;
 Chisʋs Klaist im issish ona
 Aiʋlli tok oke.

[V4]
 Yʋmohmi pulla ka
 Hʋchik kancho kashke;
 Okcha̱ya na biliashke,
 Hʋsh ahni pullashke.

[V5]
 Micha oh asilhha;
 Chu̱kʋsh achukma ya̱;
 Chihowa Holitopa yʋt
 Huchema hinlushke.</lyrics>
<title>Worth of the Soul ƲIT17</title>
<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<author>Captain Joseph Dukes</author>
<hymn_number>17</hymn_number>
</song>